(NC.QuitCard
  [LAMBDA (CardIdentifier CallCloseWFlg DontSaveFlg DontRecacheFlg InterestedWindow OperationMsg 
                 QuietFlg Don'tDeactivateFlg)             (* ; "Edited 23-Nov-88 16:55 by krivacic")

